{"sn1.76:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 1.76 ","sn1.76:0.2":"8. Chetvavagga ","sn1.76:0.3":"Najiratisutta ","sn1.76:1.1":"“Kim jirati kim na jirati, ","sn1.76:1.2":"kimsu uppathoti vuccati; ","sn1.76:1.3":"Kimsu dhammanam paripantho, ","sn1.76:1.4":"kimsu rattindivakkhayo; ","sn1.76:1.5":"Kim malam brahmacariyassa, ","sn1.76:1.6":"kim sinanamanodakam. ","sn1.76:2.1":"Kati lokasmim chiddani, ","sn1.76:2.2":"yattha vittam na titthati; ","sn1.76:2.3":"Bhagavantam putthumagamma, ","sn1.76:2.4":"katham janemu tam mayan”ti. ","sn1.76:3.1":"“Rupam jirati maccanam, ","sn1.76:3.2":"namagottam na jirati; ","sn1.76:3.3":"Rago uppathoti vuccati. ","sn1.76:4.1":"Lobho dhammanam paripantho, ","sn1.76:4.2":"Vayo rattindivakkhayo; ","sn1.76:4.3":"Itthi malam brahmacariyassa, ","sn1.76:4.4":"Etthayam sajjate paja; ","sn1.76:4.5":"Tapo ca brahmacariyanca, ","sn1.76:4.6":"Tam sinanamanodakam. ","sn1.76:5.1":"Cha lokasmim chiddani, ","sn1.76:5.2":"yattha vittam na titthati; ","sn1.76:5.3":"Alasyanca pamado ca, ","sn1.76:5.4":"anutthanam asamyamo; ","sn1.76:5.5":"Nidda tandi ca te chidde, ","sn1.76:5.6":"sabbaso tam vivajjaye”ti. "}